{
  "stem": "25209.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm taking the child.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she said, all right, I'm going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Again, you know?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- I don't know what he had-- a sixth sense.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He got us out in time '48.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just before the Gottwald takeover, the communist takeover.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Before then, how-- the soldiers from the Czech army and Soviet Union, how were they treated after the war?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was going to say as heroes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's probably right-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] probably right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, they didn't rape anyone, like the Russians did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and they, they were the, you know, they were the-- what do you call them when they, when they free somebody?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Liberators.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were the liberators.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they didn't do the things that the Russians did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, the Russians were just as bad as the Germans, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was just from the Czech population.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he knew what communism meant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was the most virulent anti-communist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was really-- I mean, my mother kept a little bit of, you know-- Well, when we came, when we came to Australia, he voted for the DLP.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, you probably don't know what DLP means, but they were-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] no, I don't want to say they were fascists.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They weren't fascist.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But god, you know, Jews don't vote for the DLP, for Christ's sake.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Christ's sake-- what a nice way to put it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My mother was a little bit more democrat-socialist, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think she was just better educated than she thought.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My, my father just went, nah, whatever-- whoever is against communists, I'm going to join them regardless.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because he had such a bad time in Russia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, and he, he just-- you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He wasn't a nice, liberal, middle-class man.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
